{"id":1285487606,"question_id":3447,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"23 hours, 54 minutes","timestamp":1718161352,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1285487606/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Clear Digits","memory":"42.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public String clearDigits(String s) {\n        \n        int len  = s.length();\n        boolean[] del = new boolean[len];\n\n        \n        for(int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){\n            char ch = s.charAt(i);\n            if(Character.isDigit(ch)){\n                del[i] = true;\n\n                for(int j=i-1; j>=0; j--){\n                    char chj = s.charAt(j);\n                    if(!Character.isDigit(chj) && del[j]==false){\n                        del[j] = true;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n        for(int i=0; i<len; i++){\n\n            if(del[i] ==false)\n                sb.append(s.charAt(i));\n\n        }\n\n        return sb.toString();\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"clear-digits","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
